spec_data.Name: libnxml
spec_data.Description:
nXML is a C library for parsing, writing and creating XML 1.0 and 1.1 files
or streams. It supports utf-8, utf-16be and utf-16le, ucs-4 (1234, 4321, 2143,
2312).
